#### Preparation

To prepare for the JBS this summer you should do the following:

* get the books on NodeJS and Javascript listed on the CS152aj syllabus
* start brainstorming ideas for apps that you might create this summer
* join the Brandeis [CSJBS Facebook group](https://www.facebook.com/groups/BrandeisCSJBS/)!  
Read about speech in [Roberto Pieraccini's blog "Voice in the Machine"](http://voiceinthemachine.com)
